OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774725064
OL,3,CPetrol bombs thrown at flat in
OL,4,CBallymena
OL,6,FPetrol bombs have been thrown at a
OL,7,Fflat in Ballymena.
OL,9,FDetectives are appealing for witnesses
OL,10,Fand information following the arson
OL,11,Fattack in the early hours of Saturday.
OL,13,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "We received
OL,14,Fa report at around 3.05am that two
OL,15,Fsuspected petrol bombs had been thrown
OL,16,Fat a ground-floor flat in the Drumtara
OL,17,Farea.
OL,26,@uD@[OU
