OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774725064
OL,3,CPetrol bombs thrown at flat in
OL,4,CBallymena
OL,6,F"Officers attended the scene, where
OL,7,Fcolleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,8,FFire and Rescue Service were already
OL,9,Fpresent.
OL,11,F"On arrival, evidence of petrol bombs
OL,12,Fwas noted and the living room window
OL,13,Fwas also smashed.
OL,15,F"One person was in the flat at the
OL,16,Ftime of the incident.
OL,18,F"No injuries were reported, however,
OL,19,Fthis was obviously a shock for them
OL,20,Fand there was significant damage
OL,21,Fcaused to the interior of their home."
